  "texts": [
    "Besides the joint training mechanism with CWS, here we evaluate the contribution of the BCNN model to the proposed method.",
    "To this end, BiLSTM, BiGRU, IDCNN, and BCNN are used as the encoding layers in our joint training framework, denoted by BiLSTM-CWS, BiGRU-CWS, IDCNN-CWS, and BCNN-CWS, respectively.",
    "Thus, the encoding models of the methods are fairly compared under the same calculation scenario, and the results on the PeopleDaily, MSRA, and Ontonote4 datasets are displayed in Figure 6.",
    "Evidently, the proposed BCNN model performs better than the comparison models.",
    "This indicates that BCNN model significantly contributes to the performance advantages of the BCNN-CWS model."
  ],
